title: Vakhshouri: Venezuela Not a Market-Moving OPEC Player
description: SVB Energy International President & Founder Sara Vakhshouri says Venezuela is not a market-moving OPEC player today, and that OPEC+ is not concerned. She speaks with Haslinda Amin on "Insight with Haslinda Amin." (Source: Bloomberg)
